    "headline": "Best Buy (NYSE:BBY) Beats Q1 CY2026 Sales Expectations, Stock Soars",
    "summary": "Electronics retailer Best Buy (NYSE:BBY) reported Q1 CY2026 results beating Wall Street’s revenue expectations, with sales up 1.9% year on year to $8.94 billion. The company expects the full year’s revenue to be around $41.65 billion, close to analysts’ estimates. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.28 per share was 4.3% above analysts’ consensus estimates.",
